text: Carlos Jaime Alazraqui (born July 20, 1962) is an American stand-up comedian, actor, and voice artist, best known for playing Deputy James Garcia in Reno 911!. He's also known as the voice of Rocko in Rocko's Modern Life, Denzel Crocker in The Fairly OddParents, Walden in Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!, Carlos and Sergio in The Casagrandes. He was also the original voice of Spyro from the Spyro the Dragon video game series. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from New York (state) Category:People from Yonkers, New York
